WEBVTT

00:01.697 --> 00:04.961
Wow, I remember this,
this is Reese's fifth birthday.

00:05.048 --> 00:06.702
This must be Christmas
the same year.

00:06.789 --> 00:08.921
He grew up so fast.

00:09.009 --> 00:10.271
He sure did.

00:10.358 --> 00:12.621
Here's Malcolm's
first day at school.

00:12.708 --> 00:14.275
Oh...

00:14.362 --> 00:17.539
Remember when we lost Dewey
at the flea market.

00:17.626 --> 00:19.671
Still keeps great time.

00:20.846 --> 00:22.848
You want to go
through the arrest reports?

00:22.935 --> 00:24.763
I'll pour
some more wine.

00:26.765 --> 00:29.812
♪ Yes, no, maybe ♪

00:29.899 --> 00:32.119
♪ I don't know ♪

00:32.206 --> 00:35.470
